Title: popup_menu.js: remembering the selected color in the Graph rendering options
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1576671172
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

 In the Graph rendering options under the Display options, the previous version
 reset the color to white every time the toggle popup menu was closed and
 reopened. This change now allows to remember the last selected color option.
